Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您只派了几个新人去追佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.35,0:01:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子的现状也不容乐观
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也采取了一些相应的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务已经决定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把事情处理完就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助离开了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经有两天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前去追赶的鸣人他们也没有消息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连小李也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大致情况我已经了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果鸣人和佐助有个三长两短的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:02:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通灵之术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先四下分散追踪鸣人和佐助的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人和佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个家伙到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具体情况稍后再做说明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先处理正事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认他们的气味后通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会立刻赶过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾亲眼目睹过他们的对决
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在让她别担心也不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别总是想着复仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便复仇成功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下的也只有空虚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在我面前摆出一副什么都知道的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我都很不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点毫无疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不是最不幸的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是都找到最重要的伙伴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为曾经失去才会了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之所以教你千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为你有了最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是用来攻击同伴或者复仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该如何去运用它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可能真的会置对方于死地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也正如你所愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在卡卡西和小樱都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会像上次那样被人阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我们一定要做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打到你求饶为止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算痛扁你一顿也要带你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 你是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助当时用这种口气对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我想用螺旋丸来确认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能和我全力发出的千鸟不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那招…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 你究竟有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的极限是两发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大致就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是超过了两发 又会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要发动第三发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你勉强发动忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非但无法顺利使出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查克拉还会归零
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好会送命的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 不能再做无谓的攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续刚才那样的势均力敌毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经完全确定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想置我于死地…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先用快招和忍术扰乱他的行动找到破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用千鸟作最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果同为一流的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要交手过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能彼此看穿对方的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便嘴上不说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太天真了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看穿我真正的心思了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁.凤仙火之术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你总是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初我知道有人和我一样后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得好安心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我一直想和你说话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 始终没能开口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都在行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且一直很受大家欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你我相差太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不甘心并视你为自己的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你越叫我拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越不想输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使进入了第七班以后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一切如旧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很固执
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有说出真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实我真的很想变得和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我…憧憬的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想和你分个高下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时 我真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那是你第一次认同我所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我即便不用交手也能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然嘴上没说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们…是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却真的想置我于死地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在连你刚才说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:15:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真是假都分不清
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许只有我一厢情愿地…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正当你是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今已经晚了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真是这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太没面子了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 这也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不明白这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…被大蛇丸带走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然用左手挡住了我对心脏的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在已经没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经使不出刚才的招式了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股不断涌出的红色查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪儿来这么强的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
